            <figcaption class="mono">真实地形系统原始截图 · demos/v3-converged/geo-system.html</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ============ 08 克制基因 ============ -->
      <section class="sec mc-reveal">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <span class="mono sec-no">08</span>
          <div class="sec-title-row"><h2 class="sec-title">一个反成瘾的收藏产品</h2><span class="mono sec-en">THE PRODUCT, RESTRAINED</span></div>
          <span class="sec-desc">克制基因 · 7+1 维度 · 北极星不选 DAU</span>
        </div>
